Produce `$PLANROOT/current_objective/member_name_overview.md`, a human-editable and AI-readable inventory of every class and struct in the project, including the file where each type is defined, its current member variable names, and the proposed modern member name for each candidate. The inventory must distinguish private/protected class members that should become `snake_case_` from public struct members that should become `snake_case` without a trailing underscore.
